name|The|Internship}}''\n| Male Interviewer\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[The Smurfs 2]]''\n| Baker Smurf\n| Voice role\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Saving Mr. Banks]]''\n| [[Robert B. Sherman]]\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''{{sortname|The|Amazing Spider-Man 2}}''\n| [[Alistair Smythe]]\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[Community (TV series)|Community]]''\n| Mr. Egypt\n| Episode: \"[[Basic Sandwich]]\" (cameo)\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[The Newsroom (U.S. TV series)|The Newsroom]]''\n| Lucas Pruit\n| Television series<br/>4 episodes\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Arthur (TV series)|Arthur]]''\n| MC\n| Episode: \"The Last Day\" (voice)\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[The Founder]]''\n| [[Harry J. Sonneborn]]\n|\n|-\n| 2016\u20132018\n| ''[[Crazy Ex-Girlfriend]]''\n| Himself\n| Episodes: \"Josh and I Go to Los Angeles\" (cameo), \"Oh, Nathaniel, It's On!\" (cameo)\n|-\n| TBA\n| ''[[Vengeance (upcoming film)|Vengeance]]''\n| Ben Manalowitz\n| Filming\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+ Roles as a writer\n! Year\n! Title\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Notes\n|-\n| 2001\u20132002\n| ''[[Raising Dad]]''\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| 2005\u20132012\n| ''{{sortname|The|Office|The Office (U.S. TV series)}}''\n| Episodes written:\n# \"[[Diversity Day (The Office)|Diversity Day]]\" (March 29, 2005) \u2013 Season 1\n# \"[[Sexual Harassment (The Office)|Sexual Harassment]]\" (September 27, 2005) \u2013 Season 2\n# \"[[The Fire (The Office)|The Fire]]\" (October 11, 2005) \u2013 Season 2\n# \"[[Boys and Girls (The Office)|Boys and Girls]]\" (February 2, 2006) \u2013 Season 2\n# \"[[Initiation (The Office)|Initiation]]\" (October 19, 2006) \u2013 Season 3\n# \"[[Safety Training]]\" (April 12, 2007) \u2013 Season 3\n# \"[[Local Ad]]\" (October 25, 2007) \u2013 Season 4\n# \"[[Chair Model]]\" (April 17, 2008) \u2013 Season 4\n# \"[[Prince Family Paper]]\" (January 22, 2009) \u2013 Season 5\n# \"[[Dream Team (The Office)|Dream Team]]\" (April 9, 2009) \u2013 Season 5\n# \"[[Happy Hour (The Office)|Happy Hour]]\" (March 25, 2010) \u2013 Season 6\n# \"[[Counseling 