{"title_page": "Family Style (TV series)", "text_new": "{{Infobox television\n| num_series         = Family Style\n| country        = United States\n| language       = English\n| channel        = [[Food Network]]\n| picture_format = [[1080i]] ([[High-definition television|HDTV]])\n| first_aired    = {{Start date|2010|8|22}}\n| last_aired     = {{End date|2010|9|21}}\n| num_seasons    = 1\n| num_episodes   = 6\n}}\n'''''Family Style''''' is a [[reality television]] series that premiered on [[Food Network]], on August 26, 2010. The show centers around an Italian restaurateur family \"The Maggiore's\" based in [[Carlsbad, California]]. The series focuses on brother and sister combo Joey and Melissa opening their first restaurant \"Tommy V's\" together. Melissa is the more strait-laced one and is in charge of running the restaurant. Joey is the flashy one who is in charge of cooking in the kitchen. Their two different styles constantly bump heads.<ref>{{cite web|title=Family Style: Latest News|url=http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/family-style/299617|accessdate=27 October 2012}}</ref>\n\n==Episodes==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"width:72%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background-color: #00CED1; color: #000000;\"| No.\n! style=\"background-color: #00CED1; color: #000000;\"| Title\n! style=\"background-color: #00CED1; color: #000000;\"| Original air date\n|-\n{{Episode list\n |Title=  The Grand Opening\n |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2010|8|22}}\n | EpisodeNumber = 1\n |ShortSummary=\n |LineColor = 00CED1\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |Title= Big Dates\n |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2010|8|26}}\n | EpisodeNumber =2\n |ShortSummary=\n |LineColor = 00CED1\n}}\n\n{{Episode list\n |Title= Rappin' Restaurant\n |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2010|9|2}}\n | EpisodeNumber =3\n |ShortSummary=\n |LineColor = 00CED1\n}}\n\n{{Episode list\n |Title= VIPs (Very Important Parties)\n |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2010|9|7}}\n | EpisodeNumber =4\n |ShortSummary=\n |LineColor = 00CED1\n}}\n\n{