for a writing session.\" Saxe added \"Writing this song with Julia was one of the most creative experiences of my life. We wrote it the day we met and recorded it that same day.\"<ref name=\"Billboard\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8533210/jp-saxe-julia-michaels-if-the-world-was-ending-video |title=JP Saxe & Julia Michaels Prepare For the Apocalypse in 'If The World Was Ending' Video: Watch |website=Billboard|date= October 17, 2019|accessdate=November 21, 2019}}</ref>\n\nMichaels said \"The song is about that person in your life who you would come back to if the world was ending, when nothing else matters and there is nothing left to hold you back.\"<ref name=\"Billboard\"/>\n\n==Track listing==\n'''Digital download'''\n# \"If the World Was Ending\" \u2013 3:28\n\n'''Remixes'''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/au/album/if-the-world-was-ending-feat-julia-michaels-remixes-single/1499729618|title=If the World Was Ending (Remixes) \u2013 Single by JP Saxe on Apple Music|website=Apple Music|date=January 31, 2020|accessdate=March 21, 2020}}</ref>\n# \"If the World Was Ending\" ([[Marian Hill]] remix) \u2013 3:27\n# \"If the World Was Ending\" (Other remix) \u2013 2:29\n# \"If the World Was Ending\" (Original) \u2013 3:28\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2019\u20132020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australia ([[ARIA Charts|ARIA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2020/1/aria-chart-watch-560/|title=ARIA Chart Watch #560|publisher=auspOp|date=January 18, 2020|accessdate=January 18, 2020}}</ref>\n| 97\n|-\n{{single chart|Austria|65|artist=JP Saxe feat. Julia Michaels|song=If the World Was Ending|rowheader=true|accessdate=January 16, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Flanders|13|artist=JP Saxe feat. Julia Michaels|song=If the World Was Ending|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 4, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Wallonia Ti